OL,6,F's Infrastructure Minister has
OL,7,Fconfirmed that the island will submit
OL,8,Fa bid to host the NatWest
OL,9,FInternational in 2035.
OL,11,FThe biennial multi-sports competition
OL,12,Fattracts thousands of visiting
OL,13,Fathletes and support staff from across
OL,14,Fthe globe and was last held in Jersey
OL,15,Fin 2015.
