OL,3,CPlans for Jersey to host Island Games
OL,4,Cin 2035
OL,6,FThe island's Infrastructure Minister,
OL,7,FConstable Andy Jehan, said: "The
OL,8,FCouncil of Ministers last week agreed
OL,9,Ffor us to write to the Island Games to
OL,10,Fexpress an interest in hosting the
OL,11,FGames in 2035.
OL,13,F"There's a huge amount of work to do
OL,14,Fbetween now and a formal bid, but I'm
OL,15,Fdelighted to have taken the first
OL,16,Fsteps."
OL,18,FLucy O'Sullivan competed as an archer
OL,19,Fwhen Jersey last hosted the Games.
