OL,6,FShe explained: "There's just something
OL,7,Fparticularly special about being at
OL,8,Fhome.
OL,10,F"Even things like walking into the
OL,11,FRoyal Yacht with your medals after the
OL,12,Fclosing ceremony and everyone cheering
OL,13,Fand clapping for Jersey's own, there
OL,14,Fwas just something really unique and
OL,15,Fspecial about that."
OL,17,FThe Infrastructure Minister hopes that
OL,18,Fhosting the event could help boost
OL,19,Finvestment in sporting facilities
OL,20,Facross Jersey.
