OL,7,Fits visitor levels bounce back to pre-
OL,8,Fpandemic levels during that year, .
OL,10,FJon Marley, Chairman of the Guernsey
OL,11,FIsland Games Association, explained:
OL,12,F"All of the hotels were full for that
OL,13,Fweek of July but it's bringing the
OL,14,Fcommunity together, that's the main
OL,15,Fthing."
